- cs.TL (Temporal Logic) is a possibility as the paper mentions "potential valuability" which could be related to temporal logic.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possibility as the paper deals with reduction rules and standardization, which are concepts related to formal languages and automata theory.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with semantic properties of the calculus, which could be relevant to software engineering.
